{"tid":1758253,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"原來屯門安定選區江鳳儀反口唔比年輕人接棒","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T13:54:40.000Z","uid":153318,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6a1d1126d0d3581256a28991e23a637bf025fe","tid":1758253,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"屯碼牛牛fb<br />\n<br />\n街坊報料：<br />\n雖然呢單料非屯碼事，而係在安定發生，但如果屬實，都係屯門政黨政治中一件大事！原來安定選區本來係想派年輕人黃泳希出選，替江鳳儀接棒，黃在當區努力做地區工作2年，直至本年10月江突然變掛，宣佈要角逐連任，令黃泳希2年付出的辛勞付諸流水。小編知道此事時，內心替黃感不值。因為從政者，違反政治承諾，係多麼缺德，又怎能有資格可以繼續服務社區呢？！<br />\n<br />\n其實早於選舉前，小編已從街坊口中收到此單料。但為免妨礙選舉公平，也不想益左建制派，所以小編無post出來。現在，一切已成定局，江鳳儀已勝出，先俾屯門牛牛去了解一下！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWP9b20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWP9b20.jpg&h=6a1c019f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfZ9b21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfZ9b21.jpg&h=3b47b426&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Ogzn9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Ogzn9H.jpg&h=6bd4eba6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57ef5a081206b38da1c32c874742ef523fb8cf12","tid":1758253,"uid":16689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"民協真係抵滅黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ed768839321d4c381a1be480a3c85809389094","tid":1758253,"uid":180609,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:47:17.000Z","msg":"老女人仲想霸住個位幾耐？出世到而家一眼都冇見過佢出現係邨內，反而個肥仔日見夜見到係邨內宣傳又好做野又好。"},{"pid":"004e436f34090c134ebe0008bcdeaa9e3953ec14","tid":1758253,"uid":153318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"57ef5a081206b38da1c32c874742ef523fb8cf12","tid":1758253,"uid":16689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"民協真係抵滅黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1